&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a clinical band 6 sister/ charge nurse on Ward 41 – a Hyper-Acute Stroke Unit. Ward 41 comprises of 36 beds for acute stroke patients and for the acute treatment of FAST positive patients requiring thrombolysis. The successful candidate is required to have excellent communication skills and must be able to provide clinical leadership and support.&lt;/p&gt;
